## 핵심 변경사항

### 1. import 추가
```typescript
import {
  fetchMedications,
  createMedication,
  updateMedication,
  deleteMedication,
  fetchMedicationLogs,
  toggleMedicationLog,
  type MedicationAPI,
  type MedicationLogAPI,
} from '../../src/lib/api';
import { useCallback, useEffect } from 'react';
```

### 2. InjectionScreen 상태 관리 변경
```typescript
// 기존
const [medications, setMedications] = useState<Medication[]>([]);
const [logs, setLogs] = useState<MedLog[]>([]);

// 변경 후
const [medications, setMedications] = useState<Medication[]>([]);
const [logs, setLogs] = useState<MedLog[]>([]);
const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true);
const [error, setError] = useState<string | null>(null);
```

### 3. API → local state 변환 함수 추가
```typescript
function apiToMedication(m: MedicationAPI): Medication {
  return {
    id: m.id,
    name: m.name,
    form: m.form as MedForm,
    dosage: m.dosage,
    frequency: m.frequencyType as FreqType,
    frequencyDays: m.frequencyDays,
    schedules: m.schedules.map(s => ({ id: s.id, timeSlot: s.timeSlot as TimeSlot, timeDetail: s.timeDetail })),
    condition: m.condition as MealCondition,
    memo: m.memo,
    colorIndex: m.colorIndex,
    isActive: m.isActive,
    createdAt: m.createdAt,
  };
}

function apiToLog(l: MedicationLogAPI): MedLog {
  return {
    id: l.id,
    medicationId: l.medicationId,
    scheduleId: l.scheduleId,
    date: l.date,
    status: l.status as LogStatus,
    checkedAt: l.checkedAt,
  };
}
```

### 4. useEffect로 초기 데이터 로드
```typescript
const loadData = useCallback(async () => {
  setLoading(true);
  setError(null);
  try {
    const [meds, logsData] = await Promise.all([
      fetchMedications(),
      fetchMedicationLogs({
        startDate: getDateKey(new Date(Date.now() - 7 * 86400000)),
        endDate: getDateKey(new Date(Date.now() + 7 * 86400000)),
      }),
    ]);
    setMedications(meds.map(apiToMedication));
    setLogs(logsData.map(apiToLog));
  } catch (err) {
    setError('데이터를 불러오지 못했습니다.');
  } finally {
    setLoading(false);
  }
}, []);

useEffect(() => { loadData(); }, [loadData]);
```

### 5. toggleCheck → API 호출
```typescript
const toggleCheck = async (medicationId: string, scheduleId: string, date = getDateKey(new Date())) => {
  // 기존 로컬 토글 로직은 유지하되, API 호출 추가
  // 낙관적 업데이트: 로컬 먼저 업데이트 후 API 호출
  // API 실패 시 error 알림 (롤백은 loadData로)
  try {
    const updatedLog = await toggleMedicationLog(medicationId, scheduleId, date);
    setLogs(prev => {
      const filtered = prev.filter(l => !(l.medicationId === medicationId && l.scheduleId === scheduleId && l.date === date));
      return [...filtered, apiToLog(updatedLog)];
    });
  } catch (err) {
    Alert.alert('오류', '복약 기록 업데이트에 실패했습니다.');
  }
};
```
단, C-5 체크 해제 확인 Alert는 기존대로 유지.

### 6. handleAddMedication → API 호출
```typescript
const handleAddMedication = async (draft: MedDraft) => {
  if (editingMedicationId) {
    const updated = await updateMedication(editingMedicationId, {
      name: draft.name, form: draft.form, dosage: draft.dosage,
      frequencyType: draft.frequency, frequencyDays: draft.frequencyDays,
      schedules: draft.schedules.map(s => ({ timeSlot: s.timeSlot, timeDetail: s.timeDetail })),
      condition: draft.condition, memo: draft.memo,
    });
    setMedications(prev => prev.map(m => m.id === editingMedicationId ? apiToMedication(updated) : m));
    setEditingMedicationId(null);
    setScreen('main');
  } else {
    const created = await createMedication({
      name: draft.name, form: draft.form, dosage: draft.dosage,
      frequencyType: draft.frequency, frequencyDays: draft.frequencyDays,
      schedules: draft.schedules.map(s => ({ timeSlot: s.timeSlot, timeDetail: s.timeDetail })),
      condition: draft.condition, memo: draft.memo,
      colorIndex: medications.length % COLORS.length,
    });
    setMedications(prev => [...prev, apiToMedication(created)]);
    // C-3 연속 등록 Alert 유지
    Alert.alert('등록 완료', '다른 약도 등록하시겠어요?', [
      { text: '완료', onPress: () => setScreen('main') },
      { text: '계속 추가', onPress: () => setScreen('add') },
    ]);
  }
};
```

### 7. handleDeleteMedication → API 호출
```typescript
const handleDeleteMedication = async (id: string) => {
  await deleteMedication(id);
  setMedications(prev => prev.filter(m => m.id !== id));
  setLogs(prev => prev.filter(l => l.medicationId !== id));
};
```

### 8. 로딩/에러 화면
- loading === true이면 간단한 로딩 뷰 (ActivityIndicator + '불러오는 중...')
- error !== null이면 에러 뷰 (재시도 버튼 → loadData())

